description: Husky Hot Dogs is serving up hungry Alaskans with a heavenly selection of highly-quality NY-style all-beef hot dogs. The folks of Fairbanks just love this cart's delicious selection of handheld grub, like the Red Hot, The Smoked Salmon Dog (yep, that’s right!), the Reindeer Dog, and so much more.Come hang out with Husky Hot Dogs, heap on some tasty toppings, and have yourself a happy, hearty day.
name: Husky Hot Dogs
